questions.quote: Damn it, Elaine. That wasn't Zach. That was the yam-yam. Now, he is going cold turkey.  And you will be at his side.
I don't even know what they think. That's why I'm in therapy.
No, I haven't worn this jacket since I got it back from the dry-cleaner. Maybe we should ask him.
Right. Well if you need an extra set of hands, I know who you can call--
[To Jerry] Oh, remind me to talk to you about something later.
What kind of stupid show is this? Hey! It's that idiot that took all my records!
Well, maybe next time someone's in a car accident you won't stop off for candy first.
Do I smell something? What am I, hard of smelling? Of *course* I smell something.
Ya, then maybe baldness will catch on. This will all be turning your way.
Why don't you sit down, Poppie? You're still recuperating.  What, are you tired, Poppie?
